584
00:47:04,167 --> 00:47:06,300
How about Okonomiyaki?

585
00:47:06,467 --> 00:47:08,933
Yes, your Okonomiyaki.
I haven't eaten it for a while.

586
00:47:09,100 --> 00:47:11,533
You like my takoyaki, too.

587
00:47:18,700 --> 00:47:22,000
<i>Right now Irie is...</i>

588
00:47:27,133 --> 00:47:28,667
Kotoko?

589
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:30,600
Are you okay?

590
00:47:31,300 --> 00:47:32,933
Why am I not?

591
00:47:33,633 --> 00:47:35,600
Where do you want to go today?

592
00:47:35,667 --> 00:47:37,633
